30:10.542 --> 30:12.054
The kids.

30:15.217 --> 30:16.091
You.

30:17.511 --> 30:18.911
You all saved my life.

30:19.665 --> 30:22.431
Got me out
of a terrible marriage.

30:22.482 --> 30:24.633
