of my favorite Fleetwood Mac song.

30:53.129 --> 30:54.480
Great, Rachel. Which one?

30:54.564 --> 30:55.797
"Go Your Own Way."

30:55.827 --> 30:57.153
It's the song about the painful breakup

30:57.183 --> 30:59.735
