Holier Than Thou Cemetery?

39:03.895 --> 39:05.038
No comment.

39:05.076 --> 39:09.417
Any comment on the fact when I looked up the I.
P. address of the person who posted the rumor

39:09.447 --> 39:11.208
I found out it was you?

39:12.066 --> 39:13.875
My computer was stolen.

39:14.332 --> 39:17.080
